By CaptianKornFlake

The CK 7 Bullfinch (Far left) is a medium altitude plane good for anything you want to use it for (Inside the atmosphere ) It boasts 1 whole turbojet engine and enough fuel to travel to other continents. It is a pretty average but use full plane. (Feel free to add missiles and bombs and show me the results).
